-- Title      : Acquisition Trigger Logic
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Author     : Lucas Maziero Russo
-- Company    : CNPEM LNLS-DIG
-- Created    : 2015-19-08
-- Platform   : FPGA-generic
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Description: Acquisition trigger logic for hardware trigger (external and data),
