------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Title      : BPM Flow Control Source module
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Author     : Lucas Maziero Russo
-- Company    : CNPEM LNLS-DIG
-- Created    : 2013-22-10
-- Platform   : FPGA-generic
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Description: Implments a simple Flow Control module
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Copyright (c) 2013 CNPEM
